<subSubSection id="08609F1843C3F125DFC43F81D38DBC5D" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="4756D432A1E0161C50AE20EF6EF2CA90" pageNumber="63">
Remarks. 
<taxonomicName id="3D229329FD6397515797A5752D3E379B" LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:E80528E6-4EC5-48D2-9B49-38E85C7886AF" authority="Günther, 1867" authorityName="Günther" authorityYear="1867" class="Teleostei" family="Cichlidae" genus="Neetroplus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Neetroplus Günther 1867:603" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="63" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Neetroplus</taxonomicName>
is hereby synonymized, so 
<taxonomicName id="819ECDAF404141E8A2A60A8F58E11F70" LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:7A9BA3FB-1462-4C73-A40A-F9A660B3AA90" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cichlidae" genus="Hypsophrys" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Hypsophrys Agassiz 1859:408" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="63" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Hypsophrys</taxonomicName>
is no longer monotypic. The other species assigned to 
<taxonomicName id="775326D748A23B3D3639B177EDBBC3D6" LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:E80528E6-4EC5-48D2-9B49-38E85C7886AF" authority="Günther, 1867" authorityName="Günther" authorityYear="1867" class="Teleostei" family="Cichlidae" genus="Neetroplus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Neetroplus Günther 1867:603" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="63" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Neetroplus</taxonomicName>
by some recent authors, 
<taxonomicName id="1E937B2BB32EFFBA4CB4238D41B94221" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cichlidae" genus="Cryptoheros" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="63" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="panamensis">Cr. panamensis</taxonomicName>
, is here regarded to belong in 
<taxonomicName id="1F43E09A134E02C00F89350D65F8788A" LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:273F29E5-91F4-45BE-8447-659BDE8939E2" class="Actinopterygii" family="Cichlidae" genus="Cryptoheros" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Cryptoheros Allgayer 2001" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="63" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Cryptoheros</taxonomicName>
(see above).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1E5CBB38FE615CA6DE71831845502816" pageNumber="63">
The availability of the name, the identity of the type species, the status of 
<taxonomicName id="B41FC3D88EE533CA19DCCA13C55AA012" LSID-ZBK="urn:lsid:zoobank.org:act:78A238C5-DD67-4615-8467-E37D9AD456CB" authority="Fernández-Yépez, 1969" authorityName="Fernández-Yépez" authorityYear="1969" class="Teleostei" family="Cichlidae" genus="Copora" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName-ZBK="Copora Fernández-Yépez 1969:[4]" order="Perciformes" pageNumber="63" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Copora</taxonomicName>
and other issues were dealt with by Kullander and Hartel (1997). Further comments below.
</paragraph>
